TextEng: "Goodbye."
"What happened to your arm?"
<StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "Tell me what happened or maybe you'll lose that other arm."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> ""말 안 하면 다른 팔도 잃게 될지 몰라.""

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "I heard some customers say you lost it because you're a coward."
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "I'd like to be your friend. Please tell me."
"I don't need your life story. Hurry up."
"What girl is that?"
"That still doesn't tell me how you lost your arm."
"Go on."
"At least you survived."
"So how did you end up working here?"
"I thought I wasn't allowed."
"Yes, please."
"I'm allowed to leave."
"I will pay you to let me out."
"No way."
"It is a deal."
<StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "You let me out, or I'll tell Durnan you forgot his instructions."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> ""날 내보내 줘, 아니면 더난한테 네가 지시를 잊어버렸다고 말할 거야.""

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "You must have forgotten. Don't worry, I won't tell anybody you forgot."
Text: <StartCheck>[허세]</Start> ""잊어버린 것 같은데. 걱정 마, 아무한테도 안 말할게.""

TextEng: "I'm <FullName>. Durnan said you'd let me out."
I found this shield with your name on it.
"Here, take this 50 gold and get your arm back."
"No, you keep your gold. You need it."
"I'll be taking the gold."
